  "Distinguished furniture for private offices, boardrooms and executive workplaces—created to bring clarity, comfort and presence to every working day.": "Arredi distintivi per uffici privati, sale riunioni e ambienti direzionali, creati per portare chiarezza, comfort e presenza in ogni giornata di lavoro.",
